quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,"Saala sa-ilun biAAathabin waqiAA"
  70,2,"Lilkafireena laysa lahu dafiAA"
  70,3,"Mina Allahi thee almaAAarij"
  70,4,"TaAAruju almala-ikatu warroohuilayhi fee yawmin kana miqdaruhu khamseena alfasana"
  70,5,"Fasbir sabran jameela"
  70,6,"Innahum yarawnahu baAAeeda"
  70,7,"Wanarahu qareeba"
  70,8,"Yawma takoonu assamao kalmuhl"
  70,9,"Watakoonu aljibalu kalAAihn"
  70,10,"Wala yas-alu hameemun hameema"